/24\/arrogant-meet-allah-wrath\/","url_meta":{"origin":2664,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Takabbur: Arrogant meet Allah while He is displeased","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever exalts himself or carries himself with arrogance, he will meet Allah while He is angry.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 5995 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2759,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/03\/angry-stand-sit-lie-down\/","url_meta":{"origin":2664,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Rage: If you are angry, sit or lie down","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to us, \u201cIf one of you is angry while he is standing, let him sit down so his anger will leave him; otherwise, let him lie down.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 5688 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10670,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/24\/husband-wife-ghusl-together\/","url_meta":{"origin":2664,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Bathing: Husband and wife bathing together","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Maymunah, wife of the Prophet, reported: I would take a bath with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, cleaning ourselves of impurities from the same vessel.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cIt is the opinion of the majority of jurists, that there is no harm for a husband and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/18\/suicide-funeral-prayer-janazah\/","url_meta":{"origin":2664,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Suicide: Praying over a Muslim who kills himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Samurah reported: A man killed himself and the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, did not pray over him. Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cThe people of knowledge disagreed on this issue. Some of them said that the Muslims should perform funeral prayers over every person who prayed towards Mecca,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11817,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/do-not-get-angry-enter-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":2664,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Anger: Do not get angry,  you will enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell me about a deed that will admit me into Paradise.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not be angry and you will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304\u00a02353 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37343,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/11\/09\/abu-darda-bidah\/","url_meta":{"origin":2664,"position":5},"title":"Abu Darda on Bid\u2019ah: Anger at seeing innovations in the religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Darda reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, entered upon me while he was furious. I said, \u201cWhy are you angry?\u201d Abu Darda said, \u201cBy Allah, I do not recognize any of the affairs of Muhammad among them except that they pray in congregation.\u201d Source: al-Bida' li-Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2664","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2664"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2664\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2664"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2664"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2664"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}